      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AYESHA BALE (1) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.75 lengths (22.74) behind Clavicle at this track. Good form should continue. KIRSTY'S CAR (8) hit the ground running last time with a strong early split and tried to lead throughout but had to settle for the minors when second (23.43) at Geelong over 400m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Expected to be in this for a long way. PAW MINTY (7) delivered a moderate run last time when fourth at this track over 390m behind Clavicle (22.97). Shapes as one to consider. NANDO TUFF (2) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
